  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA50">
<l>caṭaimēlak koṉṟai tarukaṉikaḷ pōntu</l>
<l>puṭaimēvit tāḻntaṉavē pōlu - muṭimēl</l>
<l>valappālak kōla mativaittāṉṟaṉ paṅkiṉ</l>
<l>kulappāvai nīlak kuḻal</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The fruits brought by that Laburnum on the matted hair</l>
<l>come, attached on the side, [and] hang down, it seems, on the blue locks</l>
<l>of the girl of family, at the side of him who has put</l>
<l>that beautiful moon to the left on [his] crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
